definition: to set up/to arrange/to establish/to found/to display
to have/there is/there are/to exist/to be

sentences.english: The company has agencies in all parts of Africa.
sentences.chinese: 该公司在非洲各地设有派出机构。

sentences.english: The cooling water jackets are arranged on the welding torch from the front part to the back part.
sentences.chinese: 在焊炬上从前部到后部均设有冷却水套。

sentences.english: The chairs are sheltered to ensure operation under the raining weather.
sentences.chinese: 缆车都设有遮雨棚，以确保在雨天照常运行。

sentences.english: Each room is equipped with smoking detection system.
sentences.chinese: 酒店每间客房均设有烟感报警器。

sentences.english: Shandong Provincial Hospital now has 74 clinical and medical science departments.
sentences.chinese: 山东省立医院现设有74个临床和医技科室。

sentences.english: With key type temperature supplement functions.
sentences.chinese: 设有锁匙式温度补正常功能。

sentences.english: The second floor includes a grandstand area and lounge area.
sentences.chinese: 二层则设有看台区，并配备专门的休息室。

sentences.english: Safety protection device for preventing overload of lifting cargo ladder.
sentences.chinese: 设有防止升降货梯超载的安全保护装置。

sentences.english: The factory also has grinding polishing parts of the laboratory.
sentences.chinese: 厂内还设有零部件研磨抛光工艺试验室。

sentences.english: Double zipper design handle on the cover in side pocket.
sentences.chinese: 双拉炼设计，上盖附设手抽，内盖设有透明格仔袋。

sentences.english: Consider a family of parallel lines that cut the conic .
sentences.chinese: 设有一组平行线与圆锥曲线相交。

sentences.english: And install clutch safe-device to prevent the damage.
sentences.chinese: 并设有离合安全装置，以防超负荷引起的机器损伤。

sentences.english: The Education Centre is signposted at every crossing in the college.
sentences.chinese: 该大学的每个十字路口处都设有通往教育中心的路标。

sentences.english: A time is installed that can go with all sorts of scheduled operation.
sentences.chinese: 设有自动定时装置，可配合混合时间生产作业。

sentences.english: It's a similar story at Simpson Marine, a Hong Kong-based broker that also has offices in China.
sentences.chinese: 同样，香港辛普森游艇代理在中国大陆也设有办公室。

sentences.english: Outside you can relax on a sun lounger beside the pool.
sentences.chinese: 迷人的大堂设有一个休息区和免费无线网络连接。

to set up/to arrange/to establish/to found/to display
